<HEADLINE>
<P>
LUCKY. . . AND NOT MUCH ELSE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It is inconceivable that a major network would air a miniseries which combined 
poor writing, casting, acting, directing and even makeup all in one production. 
But NBC scored a first with "Jackie Collins Lucky / Chances. " (Oct. 7-9) 
</P>
<P>
William Christiansen, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
