Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110490-0077 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 302741 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 4, 1990, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
