</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In the Arrowhead League: 
</P>
<P>
Capistrano Valley Christian 12, Calvary Chapel 12 -- Jason Sharkey completed a 
23-yard touchdowns pass to Brian Arrowood with about 2:30 remaining to give 
Calvary Chapel a tie at Westminster High. Brian Biegert rushed 29 times for 190 
yards and two touchdowns, and Darren Crail gained 133 yards in 10 carries for 
Capistrano Valley Christian (3-5-1, 3-1-1). 
</P>
<P>
In Express League eight-man football: 
</P>
<P>
