23 times for 279 yards and five touchdowns for Liberty Christian (4-5, 1-2) in 
its final game at Robinwood School in Huntington Beach. Anthony Rodriguez 
returned the opening kickoff 69 yards for a touchdown for Heritage, but 
Baltodano countered with his first touchdown, a 77-yard run. 
