COUNTY -- FINANCES; MENTAL HEALTH CARE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; EMERGENCY MEDICAL 
CARE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; PRISONS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; CALIFORNIA -- 
ELECTIONS -- 1990; LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; PROPOSITIONS -- 
