parking lot, below, was used for film's promotion. ; Photo, Crowd attending 
"China Cry" celebration sing, dance in parking lot. GLENN KOENIG / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, MOVIE SCREENED: Evangelist Paul Crouch premiered "China Cry," a 
movie about a persecuted Chinese Christian, at a glitzy promotion at Tustin 
Market Place. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
