DORNAN, ROBERT K; DANNEMEYER, WILLIAM E; PACKARD, RON; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS -- 
FINANCES; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; FINANCIAL DISCLOSURE; CONGRESSIONAL 
ELECTIONS -- 1990; POLITICAL CANDIDATES 
</P>
