actor-turned-auteur directed a cast of 500 for his $18-million epic, "Dances 
With Wolves." ; Photo, COLOR, Costner plays a U.S. cavalry officer living among 
Sioux Indians in the 1860s. An Indian village was re-created for the film. Ben 
