</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110490-0203 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 303053 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 4, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 5; Column 1; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
